high_descs: Take two rights and leave the room going to the living room take a right at the couch and go into the shelf in the bedroom.
Pick up the laptop on the shelf.
Turn right and go to the desklamp in the hallway outside of the bedroom.
anns.task_desc: Grab a Laptop and turn on a DeskLamp.

high_descs: Head round and round and walk near the shelf.
Turn right and walk near the lamp.
Turn left and pick the laptop from the rack.
Turn right and turn left and turn on the desklamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a laptop by the light of the DeskLamp.

high_descs: Turn around to exit the room and walk left down the passage to the couch and take a right turn to enter the bedroom and walk into the shelf on the left.
Close the laptop and pick it up from the closet.
Turn around to exit the room and walk to the nightstand with the desklamp.
Switch on the desklamp and examine the laptop under it.
anns.task_desc: Examine the Laptop in the DeskLamp light.
